race.description: Racing Hearts Colts, Geldings & Entires Handicap
race.comment: IMPENDOR (2) just ran into one better in a Randwick Highway when resuming and will have come on with that run now under the belt. Sure to appreciate the drop back in company here and will be right there when the whips are cracking. ABENDER (4) looked good saluting at Doomben last time out and will have derived a stack of confidence from that victory. Can go back-to-back without surprising. The well-related TEN GOOD REASONS (1) (half to G2 winner and 2xG1 placed Osipenko) may have suffered from the dreaded second-up syndrome last time out but the form prior was full of merit. Capable of bouncing right back. BUNDELLA (3) will be ready to peak now fourth-up from the break and is a must for the multiples. SIMPLY EXCELS (6) rounds out the selections.
